We are looking for an Administrative Support Officer to join our team and support our daily office procedures.
A successful Admin Support Officer will act as the point of contact for all employees, providing administrative support and managing their queries. You should be able to ensure our administrative activities run smoothly on a daily and long-term basis.

Responsibilities:

  Manage office supplies and place orders
  Maintain and update informations on company databases
  Update office policies as needed
  Organize a filing system for important and confidential company documents
  Preparation of Purchase orders/Delivery order/Invoices
  Arrange travel and accommodations
  Other ad-hoc admin duties as and when assigned

Requirements:

  Self-motivated with initiative and willing to learn
  Attention to detail
  Able to work independently and multi-task
  Strong organization skills with a problem-solving attitude
  Proficient in MS Office / Excel
  Relevant experience is a must
  Working hour 9am - 6pm, Mon - Fri
